@node FAQ_CENTER "How to post new FAQ or other things releated to FAME."

                         @{u}WHERE TO SEND NEW FAQ's:@{uu}

 If you have any ideas for additional FAQ's to add to this list here, please
 write a mail to the following adresses:

                         @{b}siegel@deadline.snafu.de@{ub}

 and post a mail with subject @{fg shine}ADD TO FAQ@{fg text}, so I'll know what this mail means.
 You could also call my BBS to post new FAQ's or to see FAME in action, the
 numbers are:

  pUNISHMENT iNC.: @{b}Node 1: +49(0) 30 694 84 70@  Node 2: +49(0) 30 694 85 70@{ub}

   Use the 'BUG' command to write your FAQs, suggestions or Bug-Reports.
  If you write a FAQ, enter as Toolname ADD TO FAQ, so I know that this 
               Report should be added to the FAQ document. 

                         Thanks for your support!

        Signed: Sascha "SieGeL" Pfalz of the FAME development team.

@endnode

